original_question: Which model saves the most gasoline? That is to say, have the maximum miles per gallon.
translated_question: የትኛው ሞዴል በጣም ቤንዚን ይቆጥባል? ይህም ማለት በአንድ ጋሎን ከፍተኛው ማይሎች ይኑርዎት።
query: SELECT T1.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id ORDER BY T2.mpg DESC LIMIT 1;

original_question: What is the car model with the highest mpg ?
translated_question: ከፍተኛው mpg ያለው የመኪና ሞዴል ምንድነው?
query: select t1.model from car_names as t1 join cars_data as t2 on t1.makeid  =  t2.id order by t2.mpg desc limit 1;

original_question: What is the average horsepower of the cars before 1980?
translated_question: ከ1980 በፊት የመኪኖቹ አማካይ የፈረስ ጉልበት ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT avg(horsepower) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE YEAR  <  1980;

original_question: What is the average horsepower for all cars produced before 1980 ?
translated_question: ከ 1980 በፊት ለተፈጠሩት ሁሉም መኪኖች አማካይ የፈረስ ጉልበት ስንት ነው?
query: select avg(horsepower) from cars_data where year  <  1980;

original_question: What is the average edispl of the cars of model volvo?
translated_question: የሞዴል ቮልቮ መኪኖች አማካኝ ኢዲስፔል ምን ያህል ነው?
query: SELECT avg(T2.edispl) FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id WHERE T1.Model  =  'volvo';

original_question: What is the average edispl for all volvos?
translated_question: ለሁሉም ቮልቮስ አማካኝ ኢዲስፔል ምንድን ነው?
query: SELECT avg(T2.edispl) FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id WHERE T1.Model  =  'volvo';

original_question: What is the maximum accelerate for different number of cylinders?
translated_question: ለተለያዩ የሲሊንደሮች ብዛት ከፍተኛው ማፋጠን ምንድነው?
query: SELECT max(Accelerate) ,  Cylinders FROM CARS_DATA GROUP BY Cylinders;

original_question: What is the maximum accelerate for all the different cylinders?
translated_question: ለሁሉም የተለያዩ ሲሊንደሮች ከፍተኛው ማፋጠን ምንድነው?
query: SELECT max(Accelerate) ,  Cylinders FROM CARS_DATA GROUP BY Cylinders;

original_question: Which model has the most version(make) of cars?
translated_question: የትኛው ሞዴል ብዙ የመኪና ስሪት አለው?
query: SELECT Model FROM CAR_NAMES GROUP BY Model ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1;

original_question: What model has the most different versions?
translated_question: የትኛው ሞዴል በጣም የተለያዩ ስሪቶች አሉት?
query: SELECT Model FROM CAR_NAMES GROUP BY Model ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1;

original_question: How many cars have more than 4 cylinders?
translated_question: ስንት መኪናዎች ከ 4 ሲሊንደሮች አላቸው?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE Cylinders  >  4;

original_question: What is the number of cars with more than 4 cylinders?
translated_question: ከ 4 ሲሊንደሮች በላይ ያላቸው መኪኖች ቁጥር ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE Cylinders  >  4;

original_question: how many cars were produced in 1980?
translated_question: በ 1980 ስንት መኪናዎች ተመርተዋል?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE YEAR  =  1980;

original_question: In 1980, how many cars were made?
translated_question: በ 1980 ስንት መኪናዎች ተሠሩ?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE YEAR  =  1980;

original_question: How many car models were produced by the maker with full name American Motor Company?
translated_question: ሙሉ ስም ያለው የአሜሪካ ሞተር ኩባንያ በሠሪው ስንት የመኪና ሞዴሎች ተመረቱ?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker WHERE T1.FullName  =  'American Motor Company';

original_question: What is the number of car models created by the car maker American Motor Company?
translated_question: በመኪና ሰሪው አሜሪካን ሞተር ኩባንያ የተፈጠሩ የመኪና ሞዴሎች ብዛት ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker WHERE T1.FullName  =  'American Motor Company';

original_question: Which makers designed more than 3 car models? List full name and the id.
translated_question: ከ 3 በላይ የመኪና ሞዴሎችን የነደፉት የትኞቹ አምራቾች ናቸው? ሙሉ ስም እና መታወቂያውን ይዘርዝሩ።
query: SELECT T1.FullName ,  T1.Id FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker GROUP BY T1.Id HAVING count(*)  >  3;

original_question: What are the names and ids of all makers with more than 3 models?
translated_question: ከ 3 በላይ ሞዴሎች ያላቸው የሁሉም ሰሪዎች ስሞች እና መታወቂያዎች ምንድ ናቸው?
query: SELECT T1.FullName ,  T1.Id FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker GROUP BY T1.Id HAVING count(*)  >  3;

original_question: Which distinctive models are produced by maker with the full name General Motors or weighing more than 3500?
translated_question: ሙሉ ስም ያለው ጄኔራል ሞተርስ ወይም ከ 3500 በላይ የሚመዝኑት የትኞቹ ልዩ ሞዴሎች ናቸው?
query: SELECT DISTINCT T2.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Model  =  T2.Model JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T3 ON T2.Maker  =  T3.Id JOIN CARS_DATA AS T4 ON T1.MakeId  =  T4.Id WHERE T3.FullName  =  'General Motors' OR T4.weight  >  3500;

original_question: What are the different models created by either the car maker General Motors or weighed more than 3500?
translated_question: በመኪና ሰሪው ጄኔራል ሞተርስ የተፈጠሩት ወይም ከ 3500 በላይ ክብደት ያላቸው የተለያዩ ሞዴሎች ምንድ ናቸው?
query: SELECT DISTINCT T2.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Model  =  T2.Model JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T3 ON T2.Maker  =  T3.Id JOIN CARS_DATA AS T4 ON T1.MakeId  =  T4.Id WHERE T3.FullName  =  'General Motors' OR T4.weight  >  3500;

original_question: In which years cars were produced weighing no less than 3000 and no more than 4000 ?
translated_question: ከ 3000 ያላነሱ እና ከ 4000 የማይበልጡ መኪኖች በየትኛው አመት ተመረቱ?
query: select distinct year from cars_data where weight between 3000 and 4000;

original_question: What are the different years in which there were cars produced that weighed less than 4000 and also cars that weighted more than 3000 ?
translated_question: ከ 4000 በታች የሆኑ መኪኖች እና እንዲሁም ከ 3000 በላይ ክብደት ያላቸው መኪኖች የተመረቱባቸው የተለያዩ ዓመታት ምን ያህል ናቸው?
query: select distinct year from cars_data where weight between 3000 and 4000;

original_question: What is the horsepower of the car with the largest accelerate?
translated_question: ትልቁ ፍጥነት ያለው የመኪናው የፈረስ ጉልበት ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT T1.horsepower FROM CARS_DATA AS T1 ORDER BY T1.accelerate DESC LIMIT 1;

original_question: What is the horsepower of the car with the greatest accelerate?
translated_question: ከፍተኛ ፍጥነት ያለው የመኪናው የፈረስ ጉልበት ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT T1.horsepower FROM CARS_DATA AS T1 ORDER BY T1.accelerate DESC LIMIT 1;

original_question: For model volvo, how many cylinders does the car with the least accelerate have?
translated_question: ለሞዴል ቮልቮ አነስተኛ ፍጥነት ያለው መኪና ስንት ሲሊንደሮች አሉት?
query: SELECT T1.cylinders FROM CARS_DATA AS T1 JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.MakeId WHERE T2.Model  =  'volvo' ORDER BY T1.accelerate ASC LIMIT 1;

original_question: For a volvo model, how many cylinders does the version with least accelerate have?
translated_question: ለቮልቮ ሞዴል፣ በትንሹ የተፋጠነው ስሪት ስንት ሲሊንደሮች አሉት?
query: SELECT T1.cylinders FROM CARS_DATA AS T1 JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.MakeId WHERE T2.Model  =  'volvo' ORDER BY T1.accelerate ASC LIMIT 1;

original_question: How many cars have a larger accelerate than the car with the largest horsepower?
translated_question: ትልቁ የፈረስ ጉልበት ካለው መኪና ምን ያህል መኪኖች ትልቅ ፍጥነት አላቸው?
query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE Accelerate  >  ( SELECT Accelerate FROM CARS_DATA ORDER BY Horsepower DESC LIMIT 1 );

original_question: What is the number of cars with a greater accelerate than the one with the most horsepower?
translated_question: በጣም የፈረስ ጉልበት ካለው የበለጠ ፍጥነት ያላቸው መኪኖች ቁጥር ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE Accelerate  >  ( SELECT Accelerate FROM CARS_DATA ORDER BY Horsepower DESC LIMIT 1 );

original_question: How many countries has more than 2 car makers ?
translated_question: ስንት ሀገር ከ 2 በላይ መኪና ሰሪዎች አሏቸው?
query: select count(*) from countries as t1 join car_makers as t2 on t1.countryid  =  t2.country group by t1.countryid having count(*)  >  2

original_question: What is the number of countries with more than 2 car makers ?
translated_question: ከ 2 በላይ መኪና ሰሪዎች ያሏቸው ሀገራት ቁጥር ስንት ነው?
query: select count(*) from countries as t1 join car_makers as t2 on t1.countryid  =  t2.country group by t1.countryid having count(*)  >  2

original_question: How many cars has over 6 cylinders?
translated_question: ስንት መኪናዎች ከ6 ሲሊንደሮች አሏቸው?
query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE Cylinders  >  6;

original_question: What is the number of carsw ith over 6 cylinders?
translated_question: ከ6 ሲሊንደሮች በላይ የሚሽከረከሩት መኪናዎች ቁጥር ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CARS_DATA WHERE Cylinders  >  6;

original_question: For the cars with 4 cylinders, which model has the largest horsepower?
translated_question: 4 ሲሊንደሮች ላሏቸው መኪኖች የትኛው ሞዴል ትልቁ የፈረስ ጉልበት አለው?
query: SELECT T1.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id WHERE T2.Cylinders  =  4 ORDER BY T2.horsepower DESC LIMIT 1;

original_question: For all of the 4 cylinder cars, which model has the most horsepower?
translated_question: ለአራቱ ሲሊንደር መኪኖች የትኛው ሞዴል ብዙ የፈረስ ጉልበት አለው?
query: SELECT T1.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id WHERE T2.Cylinders  =  4 ORDER BY T2.horsepower DESC LIMIT 1;

original_question: Among the cars with more than lowest horsepower, which ones do not have more than 3 cylinders? List the car makeid and make name.
translated_question: ዝቅተኛ የፈረስ ጉልበት ካላቸው መኪኖች መካከል ከ 3 ሲሊንደሮች በላይ የሌላቸው የትኞቹ ናቸው? የተሰራውን መኪና ይዘርዝሩ እና ስም አውጡ።
query: SELECT T2.MakeId ,  T2.Make FROM CARS_DATA AS T1 JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.MakeId WHERE T1.Horsepower  >  (SELECT min(Horsepower) FROM CARS_DATA) AND T1.Cylinders  <=  3;

original_question: Among the cars that do not have the minimum horsepower , what are the make ids and names of all those with less than 4 cylinders ?
translated_question: ዝቅተኛው የፈረስ ጉልበት ከሌላቸው መኪኖች መካከል ከ 4 ሲሊንደሮች በታች ያሉት ሁሉ መታወቂያ እና ስም ምን ይባላል?
query: select t2.makeid ,  t2.make from cars_data as t1 join car_names as t2 on t1.id  =  t2.makeid where t1.horsepower  >  (select min(horsepower) from cars_data) and t1.cylinders  <  4;

original_question: What is the maximum miles per gallon of the car with 8 cylinders or produced before 1980 ?
translated_question: 8 ሲሊንደሮች ያለው ወይም ከ 1980 በፊት የተሰራው መኪና በአንድ ጋሎን የሚፈቀደው ከፍተኛው ማይል ስንት ነው?
query: select max(mpg) from cars_data where cylinders  =  8 or year  <  1980

original_question: What is the maximum mpg of the cars that had 8 cylinders or that were produced before 1980 ?
translated_question: 8 ሲሊንደሮች የነበራቸው ወይም ከ1980 በፊት የተመረቱት መኪኖች ከፍተኛው mpg ስንት ነው?
query: select max(mpg) from cars_data where cylinders  =  8 or year  <  1980

original_question: Which models are lighter than 3500 but not built by the 'Ford Motor Company'?
translated_question: የትኞቹ ሞዴሎች ከ 3500 ያነሱ ግን በ‹ፎርድ ሞተር ኩባንያ› ያልተገነቡ ናቸው?
query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.model FROM MODEL_LIST AS T1 JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T2 ON T1.Model  =  T2.Model JOIN CARS_DATA AS T3 ON T2.MakeId  =  T3.Id JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T4 ON T1.Maker  =  T4.Id WHERE T3.weight  <  3500 AND T4.FullName != 'Ford Motor Company';

original_question: What are the different models wthat are lighter than 3500 but were not built by the Ford Motor Company?
translated_question: ከ 3500 ያነሱ ነገር ግን በፎርድ ሞተር ኩባንያ ያልተገነቡት የተለያዩ ሞዴሎች ምንድ ናቸው?
query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.model FROM MODEL_LIST AS T1 JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T2 ON T1.Model  =  T2.Model JOIN CARS_DATA AS T3 ON T2.MakeId  =  T3.Id JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T4 ON T1.Maker  =  T4.Id WHERE T3.weight  <  3500 AND T4.FullName != 'Ford Motor Company';

original_question: What are the name of the countries where there is not a single car maker?
translated_question: አንድ መኪና የማይሰራባቸው አገሮችስ ማን ይባላሉ?
query: SELECT CountryName FROM countries EXCEPT SELECT T1.CountryName FROM countries AS T1 JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T2 ON T1.countryId  =  T2.Country;

original_question: What are the names of the countries with no car makers?
translated_question: መኪና ሰሪዎች የሌሉባቸው አገሮች ስም ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT CountryName FROM countries EXCEPT SELECT T1.CountryName FROM countries AS T1 JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T2 ON T1.countryId  =  T2.Country;

original_question: Which are the car makers which produce at least 2 models and more than 3 car makers ? List the id and the maker .
translated_question: ቢያንስ 2 ሞዴሎችን እና ከ 3 በላይ መኪናዎችን የሚያመርቱት መኪናዎች የትኞቹ ናቸው? መታወቂያውን እና ፈጣሪውን ይዘርዝሩ።
query: select t1.id ,  t1.maker from car_makers as t1 join model_list as t2 on t1.id  =  t2.maker group by t1.id having count(*)  >=  2 intersect select t1.id ,  t1.maker from car_makers as t1 join model_list as t2 on t1.id  =  t2.maker join car_names as t3 on t2.model  =  t3.model group by t1.id having count(*)  >  3;

original_question: What are the ids and makers of all car makers that produce at least 2 models and make more than 3 cars?
translated_question: ቢያንስ 2 ሞዴሎችን የሚያመርቱ እና ከ3 በላይ መኪኖችን የሚያመርቱ የሁሉም መኪና ሰሪዎች መታወቂያ እና ሰሪዎች ምንድናቸው?
query: SELECT T1.Id ,  T1.Maker FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker GROUP BY T1.Id HAVING count(*)  >=  2 INTERSECT SELECT T1.Id ,  T1.Maker FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T3 ON T2.model  =  T3.model GROUP BY T1.Id HAVING count(*)  >  3;

original_question: What are the id and names of the countries which have more than 3 car makers or produce the 'fiat' model?

query: SELECT T1.countryId ,  T1.CountryName FROM Countries AS T1 JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T2 ON T1.CountryId  =  T2.Country GROUP BY T1.countryId HAVING count(*)  >  3 UNION SELECT T1.countryId ,  T1.CountryName FROM Countries AS T1 JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T2 ON T1.CountryId  =  T2.Country JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T3 ON T2.Id  =  T3.Maker WHERE T3.Model  =  'fiat';

query: select t1.countryid ,  t1.countryname from countries as t1 join car_makers as t2 on t1.countryid  =  t2.country group by t1.countryid having count(*)  >  3 union select t1.countryid ,  t1.countryname from countries as t1 join car_makers as t2 on t1.countryid  =  t2.country join model_list as t3 on t2.id  =  t3.maker where t3.model  =  'fiat';

original_question: What are the opening year and staff number of the museum named Plaza Museum?
translated_question: ፕላዛ ሙዚየም የተሰየመው ሙዚየም የመክፈቻ አመት እና የሰራተኞች ቁጥር ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT Num_of_Staff ,  Open_Year FROM museum WHERE name  =  'Plaza Museum'

original_question: find the names of museums which have more staff than the minimum staff number of all museums opened after 2010.
translated_question: ከ2010 በኋላ ከተከፈቱት የሙዚየሞች አነስተኛ የሰራተኞች ብዛት የበለጠ ብዙ ሰራተኞች ያላቸውን የሙዚየሞችን ስም ያግኙ።
query: SELECT name FROM museum WHERE num_of_staff  >  (SELECT min(num_of_staff) FROM museum WHERE open_year  >  2010)

original_question: find the id, name and age for visitors who visited some museums more than once.
translated_question: አንዳንድ ሙዚየሞችን ከአንድ ጊዜ በላይ ለጎበኙ ጎብኝዎች መታወቂያ፣ ስም እና እድሜ ያግኙ።
query: SELECT t1.id ,  t1.name ,  t1.age FROM visitor AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.id  =  t2.visitor_id GROUP BY t1.id HAVING count(*)  >  1

original_question: What are the id, name and membership level of visitors who have spent the largest amount of money in total in all museum tickets?
translated_question: በሁሉም የሙዚየም ትኬቶች ውስጥ በጠቅላላ ትልቁን ገንዘብ ያወጡ የጎብኝዎች መታወቂያ፣ ስም እና የአባልነት ደረጃ ስንት ናቸው?
query: SELECT t2.visitor_id ,  t1.name ,  t1.Level_of_membership FROM visitor AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.id  =  t2.visitor_id GROUP BY t2.visitor_id ORDER BY sum(t2.Total_spent) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What are the id and name of the museum visited most times?
translated_question: ብዙ ጊዜ የሚጎበኘው የሙዚየሙ መታወቂያ እና ስም ምንድ ነው?
query: SELECT t2.Museum_ID ,  t1.name FROM museum AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.Museum_ID  =  t2.Museum_ID GROUP BY t2.Museum_ID ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What is the name of the museum that had no visitor yet?
translated_question: እስካሁን እንግዳ ያልነበረው ሙዚየሙ ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT name FROM museum WHERE Museum_ID NOT IN (SELECT museum_id FROM visit)

original_question: Find the name and age of the visitor who bought the most tickets at once.
translated_question: በአንድ ጊዜ ብዙ ትኬቶችን የገዛውን ጎብኝ ስም እና እድሜ ያግኙ።
query: SELECT t1.name ,  t1.age FROM visitor AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.id  =  t2.visitor_id ORDER BY t2.num_of_ticket DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What are the average and maximum number of tickets bought in all visits?
translated_question: በሁሉም ጉብኝቶች ውስጥ የተገዙት አማካኝ እና ከፍተኛው የትኬቶች ብዛት ምን ያህል ነው?
query: SELECT avg(num_of_ticket) ,  max(num_of_ticket) FROM visit

original_question: What is the total ticket expense of the visitors whose membership level is 1?
translated_question: የአባልነት ደረጃቸው 1 የሆነ የጎብኝዎች አጠቃላይ የቲኬት ወጪ ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT sum(t2.Total_spent) FROM visitor AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.id  =  t2.visitor_id WHERE t1.Level_of_membership  =  1

original_question: What is the name of the visitor who visited both a museum opened before 2009 and a museum opened after 2011?
translated_question: ከ2009 በፊት የተከፈተ ሙዚየም እና ከ2011 በኋላ የተከፈተ ሙዚየም የጎበኘ ጎብኝ ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT t1.name FROM visitor AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.id  =  t2.visitor_id JOIN museum AS t3 ON t3.Museum_ID  =  t2.Museum_ID WHERE t3.open_year  <  2009 INTERSECT SELECT t1.name FROM visitor AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.id  =  t2.visitor_id JOIN museum AS t3 ON t3.Museum_ID  =  t2.Museum_ID WHERE t3.open_year  >  2011

original_question: Find the number of visitors who did not visit any museum opened after 2010.
translated_question: ከ2010 በኋላ የተከፈተ ማንኛውንም ሙዚየም ያልጎበኙ ጎብኝዎችን ያግኙ።
query: SELECT count(*) FROM visitor WHERE id NOT IN (SELECT t2.visitor_id FROM museum AS t1 JOIN visit AS t2 ON t1.Museum_ID  =  t2.Museum_ID WHERE t1.open_year  >  2010)

original_question: How many museums were opened after 2013 or before 2008?
translated_question: ከ 2013 በኋላ ወይም ከ 2008 በፊት ምን ያህል ሙዚየሞች ተከፍተዋል?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM museum WHERE open_year  >  2013 OR open_year  <  2008

translated_question: በአሜሪካ ኮድ የሁሉንም ተጫዋቾች ስም እና የልደት ቀን ይዘርዝሩ።

translated_question: የሁሉም ግጥሚያዎች የተሸናፊዎችን እና አሸናፊዎችን አማካኝ ዕድሜ ያግኙ።

query: SELECT winner_name FROM matches WHERE YEAR  =  2013 INTERSECT SELECT winner_name FROM matches WHERE YEAR  =  2016

query: SELECT count(*) FROM matches WHERE YEAR  =  2013 OR YEAR  =  2016

original_question: How many matches were played in 2013 or 2016?

original_question: What are the country code and first name of the players who won in both tourney WTA Championships and Australian Open?
translated_question: በሁለቱም የቱርኒ WTA ሻምፒዮና እና በአውስትራሊያ ኦፕን ያሸነፉ የተጫዋቾች የአገር ኮድ እና የመጀመሪያ ስም ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT T1.country_code ,  T1.first_name FROM players AS T1 JOIN matches AS T2 ON T1.player_id  =  T2.winner_id WHERE T2.tourney_name  =  'WTA Championships' INTERSECT SELECT T1.country_code ,  T1.first_name FROM players AS T1 JOIN matches AS T2 ON T1.player_id  =  T2.winner_id WHERE T2.tourney_name  =  'Australian Open'

query: SELECT T1.country_code ,  T1.first_name FROM players AS T1 JOIN matches AS T2 ON T1.player_id  =  T2.winner_id WHERE T2.tourney_name  =  'WTA Championships' INTERSECT SELECT T1.country_code ,  T1.first_name FROM players AS T1 JOIN matches AS T2 ON T1.player_id  =  T2.winner_id WHERE T2.tourney_name  =  'Australian Open'

original_question: Which department offers the most number of degrees? List department name and id.

query: SELECT T2.department_name ,  T1.department_id FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Departments AS T2 ON T1.department_id  =  T2.department_id GROUP BY T1.department_id ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What is the semester which most student registered in? Show both the name and the id.

original_question: Who are enrolled in 2 degree programs in one semester? List the first name, middle name and last name and the id.
translated_question: በአንድ ሴሚስተር በ2 ዲግሪ መርሃ ግብሮች የተመዘገቡ እነማን ናቸው? የመጀመሪያ ስም, የአባት ስም እና የአያት ስም እና መታወቂያውን ይዘርዝሩ.
query: SELECT T1.first_name ,  T1.middle_name ,  T1.last_name ,  T1.student_id FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.student_id  =  T2.student_id GROUP BY T1.student_id HAVING count(*)  =  2

original_question: What are the first, middle, and last names, along with the ids, of all students who enrolled in 2 degree programs in one semester?

query: SELECT T1.first_name ,  T1.middle_name ,  T1.last_name ,  T1.student_id FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.student_id  =  T2.student_id GROUP BY T1.student_id HAVING count(*)  =  2

original_question: Who is enrolled in a Bachelor degree program? List the first name, middle name, last name.
translated_question: በባችለር ዲግሪ ፕሮግራም የተመዘገበ ማነው? የመጀመሪያ ስም, የአባት ስም, የአያት ስም ይዘርዝሩ.
query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.first_name ,  T1.middle_name ,  T1.last_name FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.student_id  =  T2.student_id JOIN Degree_Programs AS T3 ON T2.degree_program_id  =  T3.degree_program_id WHERE T3.degree_summary_name  =  'Bachelor'

original_question: What are the first, middle, and last names for everybody enrolled in a Bachelors program?

query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.first_name ,  T1.middle_name ,  T1.last_name FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.student_id  =  T2.student_id JOIN Degree_Programs AS T3 ON T2.degree_program_id  =  T3.degree_program_id WHERE T3.degree_summary_name  =  'Bachelor'

original_question: Find the kind of program which most number of students are enrolled in?

query: SELECT T1.degree_summary_name FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id GROUP BY T1.degree_summary_name ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What is the degree summary name that has the most number of students enrolled?
translated_question: በብዛት የተመዘገቡ ተማሪዎች ቁጥር ያለው የዲግሪ ማጠቃለያ ስም ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT T1.degree_summary_name FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id GROUP BY T1.degree_summary_name ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: Find the program which most number of students are enrolled in. List both the id and the summary.

query: SELECT T1.degree_program_id ,  T1.degree_summary_name FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id GROUP BY T1.degree_program_id ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What is the program id and the summary of the degree that has the most students enrolled?

query: SELECT T1.degree_program_id ,  T1.degree_summary_name FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id GROUP BY T1.degree_program_id ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: Which student has enrolled for the most times in any program? List the id, first name, middle name, last name, the number of enrollments and student id.
translated_question: በማንኛውም ፕሮግራም ብዙ ጊዜ የተመዘገበ ተማሪ የትኛው ነው? መታወቂያውን፣ የመጀመሪያ ስም፣ የአባት ስም፣ የአያት ስም፣ የምዝገባ ብዛት እና የተማሪ መታወቂያ ይዘርዝሩ።
query: SELECT T1.student_id ,  T1.first_name ,  T1.middle_name ,  T1.last_name ,  count(*) ,  T1.student_id FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.student_id  =  T2.student_id GROUP BY T1.student_id ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What is the first, middle, and last name, along with the id and number of enrollments, for the student who enrolled the most in any program?

query: SELECT T1.student_id ,  T1.first_name ,  T1.middle_name ,  T1.last_name ,  count(*) ,  T1.student_id FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.student_id  =  T2.student_id GROUP BY T1.student_id ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: Which semesters do not have any student enrolled? List the semester name.
translated_question: የትኛውም ሴሚስተር ያልተመዘገበ ተማሪ የለም? የሴሚስተር ስም ይዘርዝሩ።

query: SELECT semester_name FROM Semesters WHERE semester_id NOT IN( SELECT semester_id FROM Student_Enrolment )

original_question: What's the name of the course with most number of enrollments?

query: SELECT  T1.course_name FROM Courses AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment_Courses AS T2 ON T1.course_id  =  T2.course_id GROUP BY T1.course_name ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

query: SELECT  T1.course_name FROM Courses AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment_Courses AS T2 ON T1.course_id  =  T2.course_id GROUP BY T1.course_name ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: Find the last name of the students who currently live in the state of North Carolina but have not registered in any degree program.
translated_question: በአሁኑ ጊዜ በሰሜን ካሮላይና ግዛት የሚኖሩ ነገር ግን በማንኛውም የዲግሪ ፕሮግራም ያልተመዘገቡ ተማሪዎችን የመጨረሻ ስም ያግኙ።
query: SELECT T1.last_name FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Addresses AS T2 ON T1.current_address_id  =  T2.address_id WHERE T2.state_province_county  =  'NorthCarolina' EXCEPT SELECT DISTINCT T3.last_name FROM Students AS T3 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T4 ON T3.student_id  =  T4.student_id

original_question: What are the last name of the students who live in North Carolina but have not registered in any degree programs?

query: SELECT T1.last_name FROM Students AS T1 JOIN Addresses AS T2 ON T1.current_address_id  =  T2.address_id WHERE T2.state_province_county  =  'NorthCarolina' EXCEPT SELECT DISTINCT T3.last_name FROM Students AS T3 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T4 ON T3.student_id  =  T4.student_id

original_question: Show the date and id of the transcript with at least 2 course results.
translated_question: የግልባጩን ቀን እና መታወቂያ ቢያንስ 2 ኮርሶችን አሳይ።
query: SELECT T2.transcript_date ,  T1.transcript_id FROM Transcript_Contents AS T1 JOIN Transcripts AS T2 ON T1.transcript_id  =  T2.transcript_id GROUP BY T1.transcript_id HAVING count(*)  >=  2

original_question: Which address holds the most number of students currently? List the address id and all lines.

original_question: Find the semester when both Master students and Bachelor students got enrolled in.
translated_question: ሁለቱም ማስተር ተማሪዎች እና የመጀመሪያ ደረጃ ተማሪዎች ሲመዘገቡ ሴሚስተር ያግኙ።
query: SELECT DISTINCT T2.semester_id FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id WHERE degree_summary_name  =  'Master' INTERSECT SELECT DISTINCT T2.semester_id FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id WHERE degree_summary_name  =  'Bachelor'

query: SELECT DISTINCT T2.semester_id FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id WHERE degree_summary_name  =  'Master' INTERSECT SELECT DISTINCT T2.semester_id FROM Degree_Programs AS T1 JOIN Student_Enrolment AS T2 ON T1.degree_program_id  =  T2.degree_program_id WHERE degree_summary_name  =  'Bachelor'

translated_question: ዜግነታቸው "ፈረንሳይ" ያልሆነውን ዘፋኞች ስም ይዘርዝሩ።
query: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Citizenship != "France"

original_question: What are the names of the singers who are not French citizens?
translated_question: የፈረንሳይ ዜጋ ያልሆኑ ዘፋኞች ስም ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Citizenship != "France"

original_question: Show the name of singers whose birth year is either 1948 or 1949?
translated_question: የትውልድ አመታቸው 1948 ወይም 1949 የዘፋኞችን ስም አሳይ?
query: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  =  1948 OR Birth_Year  =  1949

original_question: What are the names of the singers whose birth years are either 1948 or 1949?
translated_question: የተወለዱበት ጊዜ 1948 ወይም 1949 የዘፋኞች ስም ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  =  1948 OR Birth_Year  =  1949

original_question: What is the name of the singer with the largest net worth?
translated_question: ትልቁ የተጣራ ዋጋ ያለው ዘፋኙ ስም ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT Name FROM singer ORDER BY Net_Worth_Millions DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What is the name of the singer who is worth the most?
translated_question: በጣም ዋጋ ያለው ዘፋኙ ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT Name FROM singer ORDER BY Net_Worth_Millions DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: Show different citizenship of singers and the number of singers of each citizenship.
translated_question: የተለያዩ የዘፋኞች ዜግነት እና የእያንዳንዱን ዜጋ ዘፋኞች ቁጥር ያሳዩ።
query: SELECT Citizenship ,  COUNT(*) FROM singer GROUP BY Citizenship

original_question: For each citizenship, how many singers are from that country?
translated_question: ለእያንዳንዱ ዜጋ ስንት ዘፋኞች የዚያ ሀገር ናቸው?
query: SELECT Citizenship ,  COUNT(*) FROM singer GROUP BY Citizenship

original_question: Please show the most common citizenship of singers.
translated_question: እባኮትን በጣም የተለመደው የዘፋኞች ዜግነት ያሳዩ።
query: SELECT Citizenship FROM singer GROUP BY Citizenship ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1

original_question: What is the most common singer citizenship ?
translated_question: በጣም የተለመደው የዘፋኝ ዜግነት ምንድነው?
query: select citizenship from singer group by citizenship order by count(*) desc limit 1

original_question: Show different citizenships and the maximum net worth of singers of each citizenship.
translated_question: የተለያዩ ዜግነቶችን እና የእያንዳንዱን ዜጋ ከፍተኛ የተጣራ ዋጋ ያላቸውን ዘፋኞች አሳይ።
query: SELECT Citizenship ,  max(Net_Worth_Millions) FROM singer GROUP BY Citizenship

original_question: For each citizenship, what is the maximum net worth?
translated_question: ለእያንዳንዱ ዜጋ ከፍተኛው የተጣራ ዋጋ ስንት ነው?
query: SELECT Citizenship ,  max(Net_Worth_Millions) FROM singer GROUP BY Citizenship

original_question: Show titles of songs and names of singers.
translated_question: የዘፈኖችን እና የዘፋኞችን ስም አሳይ።
query: SELECT T2.Title ,  T1.Name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID

original_question: What are the song titles and singer names?
translated_question: የዘፈን ስሞች እና የዘፋኞች ስሞች ምንድ ናቸው?
query: SELECT T2.Title ,  T1.Name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID

original_question: Show distinct names of singers that have songs with sales more than 300000.
translated_question: ከ300000 በላይ ሽያጭ ያላቸው ዘፈኖች ያሏቸውን የዘፋኞች ስም አሳይ።
query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.Name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID WHERE T2.Sales  >  300000

original_question: what are the different names of the singers that have sales more than 300000?
translated_question: ከ 300000 በላይ ሽያጭ ያላቸው ዘፋኞች የተለያዩ ስሞች ምንድ ናቸው?
query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.Name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID WHERE T2.Sales  >  300000

original_question: Show the names of singers that have more than one song.
translated_question: ከአንድ በላይ ዘፈን ያላቸውን የዘፋኞች ስም አሳይ።
query: SELECT T1.Name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name HAVING COUNT(*)  >  1

original_question: What are the names of the singers that have more than one songs?
translated_question: ከአንድ በላይ ዘፈኖች ያሏቸው ዘፋኞች ስም ማን ይባላል?
query: SELECT T1.Name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name HAVING COUNT(*)  >  1

original_question: Show the names of singers and the total sales of their songs.
translated_question: የዘፋኞችን ስም እና የዘፈኖቻቸውን አጠቃላይ ሽያጭ አሳይ።
query: SELECT T1.Name ,  sum(T2.Sales) FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name

original_question: For each singer name, what is the total sales for their songs?
translated_question: ለእያንዳንዱ ዘፋኝ ስም፣ የዘፈኖቻቸው ጠቅላላ ሽያጮች ስንት ናቸው?
query: SELECT T1.Name ,  sum(T2.Sales) FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name

original_question: List the name of singers that do not have any song.
translated_question: ምንም ዘፈን የሌላቸውን ዘፋኞች ስም ይዘርዝሩ.
query: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Singer_ID NOT IN (SELECT Singer_ID FROM song)

original_question: What is the sname of every sing that does not have any song?
translated_question: የዘፈን ሁሉ መዝሙር የሌለው ምንድ ነው?
query: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Singer_ID NOT IN (SELECT Singer_ID FROM song)

original_question: Show the citizenship shared by singers with birth year before 1945 and after 1955.
translated_question: ከ1945 በፊት እና ከ1955 በኋላ በዘማሪዎች የተጋሩትን ዜግነት አሳይ።
query: SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  <  1945 INTERSECT SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  >  1955

original_question: What are the citizenships that are shared by singers with a birth year before 1945 and after 1955?
translated_question: ከ 1945 በፊት እና ከ 1955 በኋላ ባለው የልደት አመት ዘፋኞች የሚጋሩት ዜግነቶች ምንድ ናቸው?
query: SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  <  1945 INTERSECT SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  >  1955

original_question: How many available features are there in total?
translated_question: በጠቅላላው ምን ያህል የሚገኙ ባህሪያት አሉ?
query: SELECT count(*) FROM Other_Available_Features

original_question: What is the feature type name of feature AirCon?
translated_question: የኤርኮን የባህሪ አይነት ስም ምንድ ነው?
query: SELECT T2.feature_type_name FROM Other_Available_Features AS T1 JOIN Ref_Feature_Types AS T2 ON T1.feature_type_code  =  T2.feature_type_code WHERE T1.feature_name  =  "AirCon"

original_question: Show the property type descriptions of properties belonging to that code.
translated_question: የዚያ ኮድ ንብረት የሆኑ ንብረቶች የንብረት አይነት መግለጫዎችን አሳይ።
query: SELECT T2.property_type_description FROM Properties AS T1 JOIN Ref_Property_Types AS T2 ON T1.property_type_code  =  T2.property_type_code GROUP BY T1.property_type_code

original_question: What are the names of properties that are either houses or apartments with more than 1 room?
translated_question: ከ 1 ክፍል በላይ ያላቸው ቤቶች ወይም አፓርታማዎች የንብረት ስሞች ምንድ ናቸው?
query: SELECT property_name FROM Properties WHERE property_type_code  =  "House" UNION SELECT property_name FROM Properties WHERE property_type_code  =  "Apartment" AND room_count  >  1
